{"tid":1635120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"溫哥華撐港示威被踩場　　高慧然問華裔親中候選人「點解來加拿大」？","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T16:13:12.000Z","uid":224066,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd56bdf33a21694d2025f2f3697967395f046e8c","tid":1635120,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/ko-waiyin-question.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Fko-waiyin-question.jpg&h=1daf6b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界各地近來都有不少示威活動，聲緩香港的抗爭行動。不過，每一次總有當地的中國大陸人踩場。最令人覺得矛盾的，是這班大陸人選擇移民去其他國家。像最近，作家高慧然於加拿大就發現一名當地華裔候選人，在溫哥華撐港示威中踩場，並指西方妖魔化中國。高慧然忍不住問這位候選人，中國這麼好，為什麼要來加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyo/videos/1356003104555135/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyo%2Fvideos%2F1356003104555135%2F&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=84460162\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyo/videos/1356003104555135/</a>"},{"pid":"f8cf941fa91e6ad4851aa84a19eb267f0d437653","tid":1635120,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"733c493d16189dbab7dade5fcf6dfe16b99cf5f6","tid":1635120,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c163e6030c49cfa